This project performs binary sentiment classification (Positive/Negative) on Amazon product reviews using TF-IDF vectorization and Logistic Regression.

🧠 Dataset
Source: Amazon Fine Food Reviews

Total Reviews: 500K+ (sample used)

Only non-neutral scores considered:

Score > 3 → Positive (1)

Score < 3 → Negative (0)

Score == 3 → Removed (neutral)

🛠️ Pipeline
Text Preprocessing: Lowercasing, URL & punctuation removal

Vectorization: TfidfVectorizer(max_features=5000)

Model: LogisticRegression
 Confusion Matrix:
 [[11513  4866]
 [ 2093 86691]]

 Accuracy: 0.9338
 Precision: 0.9469
 Recall: 0.9764
 F1 Score: 0.9614
 MSE: 0.0662
